{"title":"Hammerhead Karoo 2 & Flora Duffy Reveal Bermuda Custom Color Kits","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/22/karoo-2-flora-duffy-bermuda-kit/","date":1626967835000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Hammerhead recently buddied up with world-famed triathlete and philanthropist, Flora Duffy, to create a limited-edition Bermuda-inspired kit for <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/08/25/hammerheads-big-new-karoo-2-cycling-computer-is-here-and-more-powerful-than-ever/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Karoo 2 cycling computers</a>. The upshot? Hammerhead siphons all Bermuda kit proceeds to the Flora Fund, Duffy’s youth-focused charity.</p><figure id=\"attachment_266184\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266184\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" alt=\"karoo 2 bermuda - flora screen shot\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1536x1025.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1920x1281.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" ezoid=\"0.44675657616984177\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-800x534.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1536x1025.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-1920x1281.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163300/karoo-2-flora-screen-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266184\">Photo: Hammerhead</figcaption></figure><h2>Bermuda Kit Design</h2><p>The low-profile casing adds clear, unobstructed viewing of the Karoo 2’s screen. It’s purely business upfront.&nbsp;But around the casing’s sides and coating the back is a vibrant smattering of chalky blues, greens, pinks, and yellows.</p><p>The palette is a direct nod to Bermuda’s pastel-painted buildings. The limited-run colorway is bold and energetic without feeling obnoxious — which, given Duffy’s apparent demeanor, seems pretty on-brand.</p><figure id=\"attachment_266187\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266187\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1.jpeg\" alt=\"bermud karoo 2 kit up close\" width=\"1124\" height=\"719\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1.jpeg 1124w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-297x190.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-800x512.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-120x77.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-768x491.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-696x445.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-1068x683.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-657x420.jpeg 657w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1124px) 100vw, 1124px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1.jpeg 1124w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-297x190.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-800x512.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-120x77.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-768x491.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-696x445.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-1068x683.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163324/bermuda-kit-1-657x420.jpeg 657w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266187\">Photo: Hammerhead</figcaption></figure><h2>The Flora Fund</h2><p>The <a href=\"https://theflorafund.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Flora Fund</a>, established in 2018, is geared to provide essential monetary support to young, dedicated Bermudian athletes through a selective grant process. The number of grants given in a year and the amount bestowed to grant recipients varies. Grants are available to both individuals and sporting organizations, regardless of age and genre of sport. To hear her describe it, the Flora Fund is Duffy’s passion project.</p><p><span><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OkyUJzcjA6U?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p>The world champion states, “I could not have successfully pursued my dream of being a professional athlete without considerable help…Now I would like to help others where I can. This is a small start but I hope to grow the foundation into a meaningful and sustainable community asset that positively impacts the youth of Bermuda.”</p><h2>Purchasing Information</h2><p>The Karoo 2 Bermuda kit ($45 MSRP) maybe not be Hammerhead’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/13/re-skin-your-hammerhead-karoo-2-gps-computer-with-new-custom-color-kits/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">loudest</a> Karoo accessory, but it is the only one that comes with a natural high, am I right?</p><p>As with any of Hammerhead’s kits, the Karoo 2 Bermuda kit package includes the casing (well, obviously), a screwdriver, backup screws (just in case), and an installation manual.</p><p>Gear nerds can kit out their Karoo 2s for the cause <a href=\"https://www.hammerhead.io/collections/best-sellers/products/karoo-2-bermuda-kit\">here</a>. Orders destined for the US or South Africa ship free.</p><figure id=\"attachment_266185\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266185\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle.jpg\" alt=\"bermuda 2 lifestyle\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1366\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-800x534.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-1536x1025.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/21163308/bermuda-2-lifestyle-1920x1281.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-conte